  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/7d6071703d2da64b74b2fcd281a817f1.avif?t=1769279112\" width=622 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Agent Fall is an action game inspired by classic titles, where you face an intergalactic government conspiracy. With aliens siding with the government, you, as an agent, must take down this dark alliance. Prepare for frantic combat, with powerful weapons, relentless enemies, and epic bosses. Do you have what it takes to expose the truth and save humanity? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play solo or with a friend! (CO-OP LOCAL)</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/8677594603b90fcf0526ba3fa4403da8.poster.avif?t=1769279112\" width=622 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/8677594603b90fcf0526ba3fa4403da8.webm?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/8677594603b90fcf0526ba3fa4403da8.mp4?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ruthless enemies and bosses! </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/31b92623dc99724db8e10362409ea597.poster.avif?t=1769279112\" width=622 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/31b92623dc99724db8e10362409ea597.webm?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/31b92623dc99724db8e10362409ea597.mp4?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse environments and playabe characters.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/efe60a75248a9c3285b785a338ef2b9b.poster.avif?t=1769279112\" width=622 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/efe60a75248a9c3285b785a338ef2b9b.webm?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/efe60a75248a9c3285b785a338ef2b9b.mp4?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arsenal of Respect!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/146cd44e2c3fc412a86a7d5b969e4e17.poster.avif?t=1769279112\" width=622 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/146cd44e2c3fc412a86a7d5b969e4e17.webm?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/146cd44e2c3fc412a86a7d5b969e4e17.mp4?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
